game.name: Sky Fight
game.description: Welcome to skyfight.io a massively multiplayer browser game. Control a fighter aeroplane trying to destroy other players planes. Each fighter is equipped with basic machine guns which can be temporarily upgraded by catching parachutes, there are upgrades for manoeuvrability, shields, speed and Kamikaze. Shoot down as many planes as possible while increasing your score and rank as the more you progress through the ranks, the more features such as custom and team games become available.
